title: Brian Keane - 3 Albums
description:
3 albums by this visionary multi-instrumentalist, composer and producer.  Drawing on influences from Sufi Dervish, deep space, celtic progressive and beyond this is very special music.  Contributers include the great Omar Faruk Tekbilek.

The albums are:

Beyond the Sky
Fire Dance
Suleyman the Magnificent- Original Soundtrack

Enjoy and please seed!;-}

Junco
